(0, 1, 'BANANA', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 10px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures;&quot;&gt;BANANA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'BANANA', '', ''),
(45, 1, 'Peach', '&lt;p&gt; A peach is a soft, juicy and fleshy stone fruit produced by a peach tree. Peace fruit is light red and sweet to have in any time of the day. Though generally peach fruit is a season based but iAvocado tries to deliver you all 365 days of the year, it specially imports the best quality peaches to reach out to ultimate consumers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: One raw medium peach (147 grams) has 50 calories, 0.5 grams of fat, 0 grams of cholesterol and sodium, 15 grams of carbohydrate, 13 grams of sugar, 2 grams of fiber and 1 gram of protein. It provides 6% of your daily vitamin A needs and 15% of daily vitamin C needs.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Peaches are considered good for digestion and to protect the eyes. They can boost your immune system and perk up your skin too. It lowers the risk of cancer and helps an individual in weight management.\r\n &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;:Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed based on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight exceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5% excess weight.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', 'PEACH ', '', ''),
(29, 1, 'Palm Treo Pro', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Redefine your workday with the Palm Treo Pro smartphone. Perfectly balanced, you can respond to business and personal email, stay on top of appointments and contacts, and use Wi-Fi or GPS when you&amp;rsquo;re out and about. Then watch a video on YouTube, catch up with news and sports on the web, or listen to a few songs. Balance your work and play the way you like it, with the Palm Treo Pro.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		Windows Mobile&amp;reg; 6.1 Professional Edition&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		Qualcomm&amp;reg; MSM7201 400MHz Processor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		320x320 transflective colour TFT touchscreen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		HSDPA/UMTS/EDGE/GPRS/GSM radio&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		Tri-band UMTS &amp;mdash; 850MHz, 1900MHz, 2100MHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		Quad-band GSM &amp;mdash; 850/900/1800/1900&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		802.11b/g with WPA, WPA2, and 801.1x authentication&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		Built-in GPS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		Bluetooth Version: 2.0 + Enhanced Data Rate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		256MB storage (100MB user available), 128MB RAM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		2.0 megapixel camera, up to 8x digital zoom and video capture&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		Removable, rechargeable 1500mAh lithium-ion battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		Up to 5.0 hours talk time and up to 250 hours standby&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		MicroSDHC card expansion (up to 32GB supported)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		MicroUSB 2.0 for synchronization and charging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		3.5mm stereo headset jack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		60mm (W) x 114mm (L) x 13.5mm (D) / 133g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', '', 'Palm Treo Pro', '', ''),
(36, 1, 'GINGER', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '', 'GINGER', '', ''),
(99, 1, 'AVOCADO OIL  WITH BLEND OF CANOLA', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;AVOCADO OIL &amp;nbsp;WITH BLEND OF CANOLA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '', 'AVOCADO OIL  WITH BLEND OF CANOLA', '', ''),
(53, 1, 'PLUM', '&lt;p&gt;Plum fruit is the perfect blend of sweet and sour in one fruit.\r\nPlums are a medium-sized stone fruit. The most popular variety has a dark\r\npurple-red skin with yellow flesh inside, both of which are edible.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: Plums primarily contain&amp;nbsp;carbohydrates, with 9.6g&amp;nbsp;(all of\r\nwhich are naturally-occurring sugars)&amp;nbsp;per 100g. They have just 0.1g fat\r\nand 0.6g protein per 100g. They are low in calories, with 39&amp;nbsp;per 100g, and\r\nhave high water content.\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;:Plums help you to lower your blood sugar and it benefits your\r\nheart health. Plums are an excellent source of vitamins, minerals, fiber and\r\nantioxidants.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;:Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\n  excess weight.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', 'PLUM', '', ''),
(54, 1, 'STRAWBERRY (per punnet)', '&lt;p&gt;New summer strawberries are one of the most famous, reviving,\r\nand nutritious fruits available. The sweet, somewhat tart berries have\r\nground-breaking cancer prevention agent content and don\'t quickly support\r\nan individual\'s glucose, settling on them a perfect decision for the\r\nindividuals who have diabetes, and a protected, delicious addition to any\r\ndiet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: One cup of sliced strawberries (100g) contain following\r\nnutritional values:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories:&amp;nbsp;32&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Water:&amp;nbsp;91%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein:&amp;nbsp;0.7 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbs:&amp;nbsp;7.7 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sugar:&amp;nbsp;4.9 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber:&amp;nbsp;2 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat:&amp;nbsp;0.3 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;:Benefits: The&amp;nbsp; heart -shaped silhouette of the strawberry is the first clue that\r\nthis fruit is good for you. These potent little packages protect your heart,\r\nincrease HDL (good)&amp;nbsp; cholesterol , lower your&amp;nbsp; blood pressure , and guard\r\nagainst&amp;nbsp; cancer . Packed with&amp;nbsp; vitamins , fiber, and particularly high levels\r\nof&amp;nbsp; antioxidants &amp;nbsp;known as polyphenols, strawberries are a sodium-free, fat-\r\nfree,&amp;nbsp; cholesterol -free, low-calorie food.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;:Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'STRAWBERRY (per punnet)', '', ''),
