(46, 1, 'Pears William', '&lt;p&gt;Williams pears are medium to large in size and have a true\r\npyriform, or pear shape, which has a large rounded base that tapers to a\r\nsmaller curved neck with a light brown stem. When mature but not fully\r\nripe, Williams pears are crunchy, tart, and slightly gritty, but when fully\r\nripe, they develop a juicy, smooth, buttery texture with a sweet flavor. A\r\npear is a mild, sweet fruit with a fibrous center. Pears are rich in essential\r\nantioxidants, plant compounds, and dietary fiber.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: One medium pear weighs around 178g contains\r\nfollowing nutritional value:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;101&amp;nbsp; calories&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;0.249 g of fat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;27.1 g of&amp;nbsp; carbohydrate , including 17.4 g of sugar and 5.52 g of fiber&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;1 g of protein&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Vitamin C&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Vitamin K&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Pears are considered good source of providing fiber, it also helps\r\nin reducing blood pressure and encourage detoxification in the human\r\nbody. It also helps repairing your damage cells and ease hangover\r\nsymptoms.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'PEARS WILLIAM', '', ''),
(47, 1, 'CHERRY (Per Punnet)', '&lt;p&gt;Cherries are the best fruits ever, they are small, easy to carry, and tastes delicious. It is packed with numerous nutrients and they are very rich in antioxidants which can definitely boost you while exercising and benefit your health.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts calories&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;in a one-cup serving of sweet cherries:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;16% Vitamin C Daily Value.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;10% Dietary Fiber Daily Value.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Grams of fat, sodium, and cholesterol.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;260. Milligrams of potassium.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: A bowl of cherry every day can change the look of your whole day! It facilitates weight loss in a healthy manner, it helps in lower your hypertension, It contains anti ageing properties which gives you a fresh look on your face. It maintains Ph levels which prevents stomach problems and indigestion.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed based on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight exceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5% excess weight.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', 'CHERRY (per punnet)', '', ''),
(33, 1, 'EXTRA VIRGIN COLD PRESSED AVOCADO OIL (250 ML)', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	EXTRA VIRGIN COLD PRESSED AVOCADO OIL (250 ML)&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '', 'EXTRA VIRGIN COLD PRESSED AVOCADO OIL (250 ML)', '', ''),
(43, 1, 'KIWI ITALIAN', '&lt;p&gt;Kiwi has a reputation for being healthy nourishment as a result of its high nutrient C content, yet the product is likewise wealthy in different supplements. These may help diminish circulatory strain, support wound healing, help keep up gut wellbeing, and that\'s just the beginning.\r\nNutritional facts: Two kiwis provides following nutrients:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 90.3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sodium: 0mg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates: 22g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 4g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sugars: 13g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 2g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;b&gt;Kiwis&lt;/b&gt; are a good source of vitamin C, antioxidants, and fiber. Antioxidants — including vitamin C, choline, lutein, and zeaxanthin — help remove free radicals from the body.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed based on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight exceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5% excess weight.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;b&gt;\r\n&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;', '', 'KIWI ITALIAN', '', ''),
(51, 1, 'Fresh Blueberry (Per Punnet)', '&lt;p&gt;The blueberry shrub is a blossoming bush that produces berries with a pale blue, purple shade — otherwise called blueberries. It is firmly identified with comparable bushes, for example, those that produce cranberries and huckleberries.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: I cup of raw blueberries provides following nutrients to human body:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 84&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.5g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sodium: 1.5mg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates: 21g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 3.6g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sugars: 15g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Vitamin C: 14.4mg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: The fiber, potassium, folate, vitamin C, vitamin B6, and phytonutrient content in blueberries supports heart wellbeing. The nonattendance of cholesterol from blueberries is likewise valuable to the heart. Fiber content assists with diminishing the aggregate sum of cholesterol in the blood and reduces the danger of heart disease.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed based on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight exceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5% excess weight.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'FRESH BLUEBERRY (per punnet)', '', ''),
