(87, 1, 'AVOCADOS ', '&lt;p&gt;Avocado fruit is defined as a large berry with a single seed. It is\r\nrich in fiber, potassium, heart-healthy fats and powerful antioxidants.\r\nAvocados can be either eaten raw or made into puddings. We can also add\r\nthem to salad, recipes and smoothies. Like we said we can add them in our\r\nhealthy diet. Why wait? When you can buy health.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: 100g of avocado fruit consist of:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 160&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 15g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrate: 9g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 2g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 7g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sugar: 0.7g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Avocado is incredible nutritious, it contains more potassium than\r\nbananas. They are loaded with fiber and eating avocados can lower\r\ncholesterol levels. It may help an individual preventing cancer and also it\r\nhelps you in lose weight.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;:Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'AVOCADOS ', '', ''),
(61, 1, 'DRAGON FRUIT', '&lt;p&gt;Dragon fruit is a tropical fruit that has become increasingly\r\npopular in recent years. Though people primarily enjoy it for its unique\r\nlook and taste, evidence suggests it may provide health benefits as well.\r\nThe most widely available variety has white pulp with black seeds, though\r\na less common type with red pulp and black seeds exists as well. Dragon\r\nfruit may look exotic, but its flavors are similar to&amp;nbsp; other fruits . Its taste has\r\nbeen described as a slightly sweet cross between a kiwi and a pear.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: One dragon fruit (100g) contains following nutrition\r\nvalue:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories:&amp;nbsp;60&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein:&amp;nbsp;1.2 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat:&amp;nbsp;0 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbs:&amp;nbsp;13 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber:&amp;nbsp;3 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Vitamin C:&amp;nbsp;3%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Iron:&amp;nbsp;4%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Magnesium:&amp;nbsp;10%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n \r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Dragon fruit is a low-calorie fruit that is high in fiber and\r\nprovides a good amount of several vitamins and minerals. Dragon fruit\r\ncontains several antioxidants that protect your cells from damage. These\r\ninclude betalains, hydroxycinnamates, and flavonoids.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'DRAGON FRUIT', '', '');
