(63, 1, 'NECTARINE', '&lt;p&gt;Nectarines have red, yellow, or white flesh &amp;nbsp; and are a source of\r\nVitamin A and C. They are commonly eaten fresh or cooked in jams and\r\npies. They are generally grown in the warmer temperature regions.\r\nNectarines are low in calories and rich in fiber. The nutrients in nectarine\r\nfruit offer health benefits in terms of improved metabolism, digestion and\r\nheart health.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: 100g of Nectarine fruit provides following nutritional\r\nvalue.\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 44&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.3g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrate: 11g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 1.7g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Sugar: 8g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Protein: 1.1gg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Vitamin A: 6%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Vitamin C: 9%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Nectarines lowers the risk of obesity, diabetes and heart disease.\r\nIt helps in lowering cholesterol and slows the growth of cancer cells. It is\r\ndefinitely recommended for a healthy diet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'NECTARINE', '', ''),
(64, 1, 'DURIAN', '&lt;p&gt;Durian is a unique tropical fruit. Durian is very high in nutrients,\r\ncontaining more than most other fruits.&amp;nbsp; It has a spiky outer shell and a\r\nsmelly flesh that can vary in color. It can be used in preparing juices, soup,\r\ncandy, ice cream and other deserts which means a healthy diet in a yummy\r\nway.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: 100g nutrition value of Durian:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 147kcal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 1.47gg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates: 27.09g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 5.33g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Fiber: 3.8g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Durian helps an individual in fighting infection and lowers blood\r\nsugar. It reduces the risk of cancer and prevents from health disease. It\r\nhelps in improving and reducing cholesterol levels.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'DURIAN', '', ''),
(65, 1, 'LONGAN', '&lt;p&gt;Longan have their edible white-fleshed fruits are somewhat similar\r\nto the related&amp;nbsp; lychee &amp;nbsp;and are commonly sold fresh, dried, or canned in\r\nsyrup. The juicy flesh has a mildly sweet and musky flavor.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: 100g of longan fruit consists of:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 60&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrate: 15g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 1.1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 1.3g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Longan fruit is considered general tonic to increase energy and\r\nboost immune system. It helps in reducing stress and further depression. It\r\nhelps in decreasing fatigue and boosting memory. It is always about self\r\nhealth and longan helps in improving one.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'LONGAN', '', ''),
