(57, 1, 'FRESH RED CURRANT ', '&lt;p&gt;Currants are identified with gooseberries and arrive in a blend of\r\nhues. They are unique in relation to the dried currants you see at the\r\nsupermarket, which are extremely simply minor raisins. The specific kind\r\nof the berries depends of the shading—red, white, or black—however they\r\nare on the whole tart and delicious. While they are sour, they will in\r\ngeneral be less sharp than gooseberries so they can be eaten raw: sprinkle\r\nthem on your morning yogurt or simply eat them by the bunch. Yet, they\r\ndo get delightfully sweet and delicious when cooked, as well.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: A bowl of fresh red currants (100g) provides following\r\nnutrition:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 56&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.2g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sodium: 1mg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates: 14g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 4.3g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sugars: 7.4g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 1.4g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Red currants can help individual fight infections and can be great\r\nfor hair and skin. It also helps in improving digestion and fights\r\nconstipation. It also increases your bone strength and makes you stronger.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'FRESH RED CURRANT ', '', ''),
(58, 1, 'MELON JAPANESSE', '&lt;p&gt;Other than offering the best rarities to extinguish your thirst, we\r\nshare the polished skill of Japanese ranchers in the quest for &quot;new and\r\ngreat nourishment&quot; for our clients. For instance, the development of\r\nShizuoka Melon applies the technique for &quot;one melon for every vine&quot;. Just\r\nthree potential melons are held on every vine. At that point, farmers will\r\nselect the best one from the three. As the selected melon ingests every\r\nsingle accessible supplement and daylight, it will without a doubt be the\r\njuiciest, best melon of the best, prepared to serve and delectable to eat.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: One cup of finely chopped melon (100g) provides\r\nfollowing nutrition values:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 16&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.2g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates: 3.67g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 2.6g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Sugars: 1.03g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Protein: 0.46g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Like most fruits, Japanese melon has high water content at\r\nalmost 90 percent. Eating the melon will keep you hydrated throughout the\r\nday, which is important for hearth health; it also helps in improving\r\ndigestion and health kidneys. It gives a healthy blood pressure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\n\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'MELON JAPANESSE', '', ''),
