(66, 1, 'Mangosteen', '&lt;p&gt;Mangosteen is an exotic, tropical fruit with a slightly sweet and\r\nsour flavor. The&amp;nbsp;fruit&amp;nbsp;is sometimes referred to as\r\npurple&amp;nbsp;mangosteen&amp;nbsp;because of the deep purple color its rind develops when\r\nripe. It is also used for stimulating the immune system and improving\r\nmental health.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: 1 cup (196g) serving of mangosteen:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 143&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbs: 35g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 3.5g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Mangosteen is considered highly nutritious and rich in powerful\r\nantioxidants. It supports blood sugar control and promoted healthy\r\nimmune system. It also helps in maintaining healthy skin with some\r\nnatural effects of fruit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'MANGOSTEEN', '', ''),
(50, 1, 'APPLE RED WASHINGTON', '&lt;p&gt;We all have always drooled over such red apples, haven’t we? iAvocado brings the best imported quality apple keeping your health in mind. Meet the world\'s most loved snacking apple. The heart-formed Red Delicious highlights a brilliant red and its striped skin. Prestigious for its crunchy surface and somewhat sweet flavor, this delicious apple sparkles in cool, fresh plates of mixed greens.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nutritional facts: Eating one large apple provides 20% of the recommended daily value of dietary fiber, 8% of the antioxidant Vitamin C, and 7% of your day’s potassium, all for only 130 calories.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: It contains no amount of fat, zero sodium and no cholesterol which means an apple is an obvious benevolent for a human body.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed based on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight exceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5% excess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'APPLE RED WASHINGTON', '', ''),
