(49, 1, 'RED/BLACK GRAPES', '&lt;p&gt;Grapes are viewed as probably the most advantageous fruitful -\r\nwatery product. Grapes comprise of a ton of nutrients, minerals, filaments\r\nand unsaturated fats. Grapes are viewed as solid for the skin, heart, and the\r\nveins. Among grapes, the black and red grapes are viewed as more\r\nbeneficial.\r\nA wide range of grapes are plentiful in supplements, particularly minerals\r\nand nutrients. Truth be told, regarding the wellbeing viewpoints, the black\r\ngrape is viewed as the most nourishing. Most wellbeing specialists and\r\nnutritionists prescribe black grapes contrasted with red grapes.\r\niAvocado imports the best quality grapes to give all our people the healthy\r\nlife.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts &lt;/b&gt;: Grapes are packed with&amp;nbsp;nutrients, especially vitamins C\r\nand K\r\nOne cup (100grams) has:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 70&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Vitamin C: 3.6mg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Potassium: 196mg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates: 18.1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.16g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 0.72g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 0.9g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Grapes are the easiest fruits to pack in your lunch box and have a\r\nhealthy meal but now you can also order to wherever you want. It helps in\r\nprotecting your heart and improving your vision. It fights with the risk of\r\nyour cancer and also boost your brains functioning. Grapes are also\r\nconsidered good for healthy skin.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight &lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', ' GRAPES', '', ''),
(55, 1, 'KIWI NZ', '&lt;p&gt;The name derives from the&amp;nbsp;kiwi, a native flightless bird, which&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;a\r\nnational symbol of&amp;nbsp;New Zealand. Kiwis are edible&amp;nbsp;fruit- or oval-sized\r\nfruits similar to fuzzy&amp;nbsp;kiwifruit&amp;nbsp;in taste and appearance, but with thin,\r\nsmooth green skin.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: One kiwi fruit (100g) has following nutrients value:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories:&amp;nbsp;60&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.5g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sodium:&amp;nbsp;3mg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates:&amp;nbsp;15g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber:&amp;nbsp;3g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sugar:&amp;nbsp;9g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 1.1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Kiwi fruits are considered good for digestion as the pulp and\r\nseeds are edible, hence it helps for a healthy stomach. It has a high source\r\nof Vitamin C, kiwis are also one of a kind who helps your skin to glow and\r\ngive you a beautiful skin.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'KIWI NZ', '', ''),
(68, 1, 'RAMBUTAN', '&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;fruit&amp;nbsp;is related to the lychee and longan&amp;nbsp;fruits&amp;nbsp;and has a similar\r\nappearance when peeled. Its translucent white flesh has a sweet yet creamy\r\ntaste and contains a seed in its middle. Rambutans are filled with vitamin\r\nC which prevents body cells from being damaged b free radicals.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: 100g of rambutan consist of:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 68&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.3g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sodium: 16mg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates: 16g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 0.3g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sugars: 13g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Rambutan helps in improving eye health and reduces bad\r\ncholesterol. It also helps in preventing cancer, cleaning kidneys and boosts\r\nan individual immunity. It is also a cure for Diarrhea and helps in lowering\r\nblood pressure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'RAMBUTAN', '', ''),
(69, 1, 'RED GLOBE GRAPES', '&lt;p&gt;While the regular green grapes are tasty and healthy, what is\r\ncatching people\'s attention these days are the red globe grapes. They are\r\nbigger in size, juicier and tastier, and may also hold many health benefits.\r\nThe&amp;nbsp;Red Globe&amp;nbsp;is a variety of very large, seeded&amp;nbsp;red grapes&amp;nbsp;with firm flesh\r\nused mainly as a table&amp;nbsp;grape.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: 100g of red globe grapes consists of:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 69&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrates: 18.1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.16g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 0.72g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 0.9g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Red globe grapes help in boosting immunity and regulate blood\r\npressure. It is also considered good for eyes. It helps in maintaining water\r\nbalance of the body and also helps in improving in heart health.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'RED GLOBE GRAPES', '', ''),
(70, 1, 'PINEAPPLE HAWAIIAN', '&lt;p&gt;A pineapple is neither a pine nor an apple, but a fruit consisting of\r\nmany berries that have grown together. Pineapple is a famous fruit as it\r\ntastes amazing, it can be used in preparing juices and salads.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nutritional facts&lt;/b&gt;: 100g of pineapple fruit consist of:\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Calories: 50&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fat: 0.1g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Carbohydrate: 13g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Fiber: 1.4g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Sugar: 10g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;Protein: 0.5g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Benefits&lt;/b&gt;: Pineapples&amp;nbsp;contain bromelain, an enzyme that may help arthritis\r\npain by easing inflammation. They are also a good source of vitamin C,\r\nwhich helps your immune system.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Variable weight&lt;/b&gt;: Kindly note all the fresh fruits and vegetables are billed\r\nbased on exact weight during order processing, in case if the weight\r\nexceeds the requested weight by 5% more then you will be charged for 5%\r\nexcess weight.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'PINEAPPLE HAWAIIAN', '', ''),
