(85, 1, 'Pomegranate', '&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-top: 25px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); font-family: &amp;quot;Proxima Nova&amp;quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, system-ui, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Pomegranate seeds get their vibrant red hue from polyphenols. These chemicals are powerful&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/301506.php&quot; title=&quot;How can antioxidants benefit our health?&quot; class=&quot;content-link css-29oowu keywords&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; box-sizing: inherit; cursor: pointer; border-color: currentcolor; color: rgb(5, 162, 211);&quot;&gt;antioxidants&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-top: 25px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); font-family: &amp;quot;Proxima Nova&amp;quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, system-ui, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Pomegranate juice contains higher levels of antioxidants than most other fruit juices. It also has&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.researchgate.net/publication/23790554_Pomegranate_juice_A_heart-healthy_fruit_juice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; class=&quot;content-link css-29oowu&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; box-sizing: inherit; cursor: pointer; border-color: currentcolor; color: rgb(5, 162, 211);&quot;&gt;three times more antioxidants&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;than red wine and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/269538.php&quot; title=&quot;Green tea: Health benefits, side effects, and research&quot; class=&quot;content-link css-29oowu keywords&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; box-sizing: inherit; cursor: pointer; border-color: currentcolor; color: rgb(5, 162, 211);&quot;&gt;green tea&lt;/a&gt;. The antioxidants in pomegranate juice can help remove free radicals, protect cells from damage, and reduce&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/248423.php&quot; title=&quot;Everything you need to know about inflammation&quot; class=&quot;content-link css-29oowu keywords&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; box-sizing: inherit; cursor: pointer; border-color: currentcolor; color: rgb(5, 162, 211);&quot;&gt;inflammation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'POMEGRANATE', '', ''),
